sys_ui_message.key: Only KPI's that have the Assignment Group and Assigned to breakdowns and are collected daily, can be associated with an KPI Group of type Assignment Group.
sys_ui_message.message: Тільки КПЕ, які мають групу призначення, призначені розбивкам і збираються щодня, може бути пов'язані з групою КПЕ типу «Група призначення».
sys_ui_message.sys_name: Only KPI's that have the Assignment Group and Assigned to breakdowns and are collected daily, can be associated with an KPI Group of type Assignment Group.
